headline: Piper Sandler Maintains an Overweight Rating on Chewy Inc (CHWY) – Here’s Why
summary: Chewy Inc (NYSE:CHWY) is one of the best e-commerce stocks to buy now. Piper Sandler maintained an Overweight rating on Chewy Inc (NYSE:CHWY) on February 5, setting a price target of $48.00. headline: 1 Safe-and-Steady Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 That Underwhelm
summary: A stock with low volatility can be reassuring, but it doesn’t always mean strong long-term performance. Investors who prioritize stability may miss out on higher-reward opportunities elsewhere.
